# ticket-reviewer - Overview (L1)

## Triggers
- "review my tickets", "what tickets need review", "check my review queue"
- Any mention of Jira reviews or verifying completed work before closing

## Workflow
1. Fetch tickets in Review status via acli JQL query
2. For each ticket: get details, comments, linked PRs
3. Verify work: check PR merged, DNS propagated, service deployed, etc.
4. Close ticket or provide feedback with specific comments

## Dependencies
- acli (Atlassian CLI - see toolkit/acli.md for location)
- gh (GitHub CLI, authenticated to github.je-labs.com)
- nslookup / DNS tools

## Self-Improving
- Check `examples/` for past reviews of similar ticket types
- Apply patterns from `learnings.md` (common review criteria, gotchas)
- After each review session, add notable examples and update learnings
